data.description: Seller has a total of 9 residential building lots for sale in The Arbors at Fair Oaks. He will sell them individually or all 9 together ($170,000.00 for all 9 lots). The lots are level, 6 in cul-de-sac, cleared, curb and gutter, utilities in place, and streetlights. This is a HOA swim/tennis community with beautiful homes all around. Three of these lots are almost an acre each. There are two basement lots. Don't miss this opportunity to build much needed homes in Rome, GA! Perfect for a builder or individual looking for a beautiful lot to build their dream home.
